@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog Detay</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .cover {
            width: 100%;
            height: 300px;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .meta {
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .meta span {
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .content {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .comments {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .comment {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .comment-author {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .new-comment {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .new-comment textarea {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            resize: none;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <!-- Kapak Fotoğrafı -->
    <div class="cover" style="background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/800x300');"></div>

    <!-- Blog Meta Bilgileri -->
    <div class="meta">
        <span>Kategori: <strong>Teknoloji</strong></span>
        <span>Yazar: <strong>John Doe</strong></span>
        <span>Oluşturma Tarihi: <strong>21 Kasım 2024</strong></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Blog Detayı -->
    <div class="content">
        <h1>Blog Başlığı</h1>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Phasellus nec iaculis mauris. Nulla facilisi. Cras tristique purus vel felis ultricies, eget feugiat nisl dignissim. Sed quis turpis vitae eros viverra tincidunt.</p>
        <p>Donec vel justo euismod, finibus tortor vel, tempus massa. Aenean blandit massa at odio ornare vehicula. Integer fermentum malesuada lacus in vehicula. Curabitur id libero et sapien varius aliquam.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Yorumlar -->
    <div class="comments">
        <h2>Yorumlar</h2>
        <div class="comment">
            <p class="comment-author">Jane Doe</p>
            <p>Harika bir yazı! Çok bilgilendirici olmuş.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="comment">
            <p class="comment-author">Michael Smith</p>
            <p>Detaylara hayran kaldım. Teşekkürler!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Yeni Yorum Yapma -->
    <div class="new-comment">
        <h2>Yeni Yorum Yap</h2>
        <textarea placeholder="Yorumunuzu buraya yazın..."></textarea>
        <button class="btn">Gönder</button>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>